<glossary>
<definition id="fs-id1167584769967">
<term>entropy</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1167584749829">state function of the system that changes when heat is transferred between the system and the environment</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-id1167584981815">
<term>entropy statement of the second law of thermodynamics</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1167584761304">entropy of a closed system or the entire universe never decreases</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>

